      "beast_baseline": "Wait, \"goblin surge\"? What do you mean by that? I'm looking for technical root causes like DB connection pooling issues or TCP timeouts. Can we stay focused on the actual infra metrics? What specific metrics should I pull to see if this is a connection exhaustion issue?",
